{"tid":915593,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【爆相爆片】傳溫哥華欠租兩個月 卓林秘密返港見阿媽","createTime":"2018-11-25T06:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T07:41:23.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c8208cfb8e4e8f94a5e403ab37a653a82508766c","tid":915593,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T06:02:55.000Z","msg":"吳綺莉嘅19歲獨女卓林舊年出櫃，承認戀上加拿大籍女友Andi，搞到母女關係惡化，之後卓林更離家出走。<br />\n今年4月，卓林同Andi飛到加拿大過住顛沛流離嘅生活，聲稱無家可歸嘅卓林，更喺YouTube拍片尋父親成龍，之後，佢又俾人影到拖住買餸車到垃圾站，疑似「拾荒」，其後有消息指，卓林同Andi喺溫哥華居住其間曾經欠租兩個月，搞到俾屋主趕走。<br />\n早前曾發訊息俾香港十幾間公關公司，表示希望可以返港後獲邀出席活動嘅卓林同Andi，原來已經返咗香港喇。今日《蘋果》讀者Bobby透過「爆相爆片」，表示下午兩點半左右，喺銅鑼灣中央圖書館附近見到卓林同Andi，片中所見，着住白色情侶裝嘅卓林同Andi，好恩愛咁手拖住手行，不過Andi就喺衫外加咗件佢至愛嘅粉紅色外套。<br />\n讀者Bobby話：「佢哋講嘢好大聲，笑得又大聲，所以就留意到。佢哋一路行一路食煙，經過嘅時候仲聞到好大陣煙味。」<br />\n據知卓林同Andi係今朝返港，吳綺莉有安排同事接機。吳綺莉接受《蘋果》電話訪問時話：「係，我內地同事去接佢，仲返咗屋企同我坐咗一陣。」係咪安心咗？佢話：「可以咁講，我感覺到佢有長大，但唔可以用我嘅年紀去比較，慢慢嚟啦。」<br />\n問到卓林係咪返屋企住？佢話：「唔係，暫時唔返嚟住。（幫佢安排地方？）身為媽咪就覺得佢哋應該學習獨立，大家都18、9歲，每個人都有迷惘嘅時候，我諗所有媽咪一樣&hellip;&hellip;但家門永遠為你打開。」吳綺莉說話含糊，但聽得出仲未接受到Andi。有指卓林同Andi喺溫哥華居住時欠租，問佢會唔會代交？吳綺莉話：「做媽媽，當然都有底線，佢朋友（Andi）都30幾歲，每個人都要承擔做事後果。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181124/large/1543060963_1d0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181124%2Flarge%2F1543060963_1d0b.jpg&h=50d1ead8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181124/large/1543060968_a426.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181124%2Flarge%2F1543060968_a426.jpg&h=8928dbad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181124/58953482\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181124%2F58953482&d=tKJvl9cJ4JGxj2E%2F8UpRZGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=a38125b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181124%2F58953482&h=e61bcbd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181124/58953482</a>"},{"pid":"d478de1a2d5b77fcc9f49aa30bbf8b71970a53ba","tid":915593,"uid":73,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T06:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/25/140636_406c2b407ffc79c8cb1d577248d02635.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F25%2F140636_406c2b407ffc79c8cb1d577248d02635.png&h=965b2941&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nmilf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fcd946b30928e1c05a3dd94a712cabd53e735c","tid":915593,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T07:09:53.000Z","msg":"呀媽都好似癲癲地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1537c31274f981ef74c52890a0c62a319c0e41","tid":915593,"uid":171594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T07:41:23.000Z","msg":"成龍出黎講兩句？"}]}